in the vengeful reincarnation of an Egyptian priest who had been sentenced to an eternity as one of the living dead.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
