        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTracy & Martina: Live\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Friday, September 25, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 8:00 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: Advance P1 $56.25 | P2 $51.25 | P3 $56.25 ~ Day of P1 $61.25 | P2 $56.25| P3 $51.25 \n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Friday, September 25, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 8:00 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: Advance P1 $56.25 | P2 $51.25 | P3 $56.25 ~ Day of P1 $61.25 | P2 $56.25| P3 $51.25 \n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tAll the way from Cape Breton Island, the girls head out on their first cross-Canada tour. Come see the viral East Coast duo as they bring their signature storytelling and off the cuff humour to the stage. If you’re missing home or just want a good laugh, Tracy and Martina deliver every time. With stories, crowd interaction, and plenty of surprise moments, it’s a night you won’t forget!\nhttps://www.tracyandmartina.com/\nVIP Meet and Greet Add-on (6:00PM) $57.50\nhttps://purchase.imperialtheatre.ca/ChooseSeats/39201\nON SALE: Friday, May 22 @ 10AM\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
