costumes, and the kind of connection that turns an evening out into an unforgettable memory.\nAnd the best part? You’re part of it. Sing. Dance. Celebrate. This is a night where the audience helps create the magic.\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
