      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tGrace, 2 – Celebrating The Tragically Hip\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Saturday, October 03, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $54.50\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Music - Rock, Tribute show\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Saturday, October 03, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $54.50\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Music - Rock, Tribute show\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tSecond Annual “Tour For the Cure” Featuring Grace, 2 – Celebrating the Tragically Hip\nIn Support of The Canadian Cancer Society\nJoin us for a night of Canadian anthems and community spirit as the Second Annual “Tour For the Cure” rolls into Saint John.\nOn Saturday, October 3, 2026, the historic Imperial Theatre will come alive with the sights, sounds, and emotions of Canada’s favourite band. Grace, 2 delivers a performance that goes far beyond a simple tribute—it is a celebration of the music that has woven itself into the fabric of our lives.\nMore Than Just Music To truly honour the legacy of Gord Downie, Grace, 2 believes we must use the power and inﬂuence of The Tragically Hip’s music to drive change. Gord asked us all to “do something,” and so we shall.\nUnited by the soundtrack of a generation, this event aims to raise vital funds and awareness for The Canadian Cancer Society. By gathering to sing the songs we love, we are also joining in the ﬁght for a future where no one has to face cancer alone.\nWhat to Expect:\n• A Faithful Tribute: An energetic, passionate performance capturing the spirit of The Hip’s live shows.\n• Iconic Venue: Experience these legendary songs in the stunning acoustics of the “most beautifully restored theatre in Canada,” the Imperial Theatre.\n• A Meaningful Cause: In support of the he Canadian Cancer Society.\nCome for the memories and to support a great cause.\nLet’s raise the roof and raise hope, together. “We don’t imitate, we celebrate. We perform to evoke those cherished memories and emotions that are forever linked to The Hip’s music, while honuoring the indelible legacy of Gord Downie.” — Grace, 2\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
      }
    ]
  },
