he biggest musical superstars on the planet. This full band musical experience with musicians from Rock of Ages will feature vocalist, pianist extraordinaire and tribute artist Jeff Brewer, who has performed internationally to large, sold-out audiences everywhere! This will be a very interactive show, inviting YOU, THE AUDIENCE to sing along to hit after hit to musical anthems that have been the soundtrack to many of our lives!\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
