        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSaint John Theatre Company: Frozen\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Wednesday, November 25, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $70 Regular | $65 Senior | $40 Student\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Community, Family Friendly, Theatre/Musical\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Wednesday, November 25, 2026\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $70 Regular | $65 Senior | $40 Student\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Community, Family Friendly, Theatre/Musical\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tExperience the magic of Frozen! Join Anna, Elsa, Olaf, and friends on an electrifying, heart-melting adventure packed with unforgettable songs, dazzling magic, and a celebration of sisterhood that will have you laughing, crying, and cheering all the way to the final note.\nSJTC Subscriptions onsale now Regular: $143 | Senior: $131 | Student: $79\nSingle tickets onsale September 1st\nPerformances:\nWed, Nov 25 @ 7:30pm\nThurs, Nov 26 @ 7:30pm\nFri, Nov 27 @ 7:30pm\nSat, Nov 28 @ 2pm\nSat, Nov 28 @ 7:30pm\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
