      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSaint John Theatre Company: Murder on the Orient Express\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Wednesday, March 17, 2027\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $55 Regular | $50 Senior | $30 Student \n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Community, Theatre/Musical\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Wednesday, March 17, 2027\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $55 Regular | $50 Senior | $30 Student \n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Community, Theatre/Musical\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tAll aboard the Orient Express for a thrilling, twist-filled ride! When a passenger is found dead, every glamorous traveler becomes a suspect, and only the brilliant Hercule Poirot can untangle the web of secrets. Fast-paced, suspenseful, and full of shocking twists – this murder mystery will keep you guessing until the very last moment.\nSJTC Subscriptions onsale now Regular: $143 | Senior: $131 | Student: $79\nSingle tickets onsale September 1st\nPerformances:\nWed, Mar 17 @ 7:30pm\nThurs, Mar 18 @ 7:30pm\nFri, Mar 19 @ 7:30pm\nSat, Mar 20 @ 2pm\nSat, Mar 20 @ 7:30pm\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
