    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Don’t miss Spamalot! A laugh-out-loud musical quest for the Holy Grail, where logic is optional and danger is rarely taken seriously. From “flesh wounds” that aren’t quite as bad as they look to gloriously absurd misadventures at every turn, it’s a fast-paced, joyfully ridiculous night at the theatre you won’t want to miss. SJTC Subscriptions onsale now Regular: $143 | Senior: $131 | Student: $79 Single tickets onsale September 1st Performances: Wed, May 19 @ 7:30pm Thurs, May 20 @ 7:30pm Fri, May 21 @ 7:30pm Sat, May 22 @ 2pm Sat, May 22 @ 7:30pm"
      }
    ],
