        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSaint John Theatre Company: Spamalot\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Wednesday, May 19, 2027\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $65 Regular | $60 Senior | $35 Student\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Community, Family Friendly, Theatre/Musical\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tLocation: Imperial Theatre\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDate: Wednesday, May 19, 2027\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShow Starts: 7:30 PM\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tTickets: $65 Regular | $60 Senior | $35 Student\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSTYLE OF SHOW: Community, Family Friendly, Theatre/Musical\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRead More\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tDon’t miss Spamalot! A laugh-out-loud musical quest for the Holy Grail, where logic is optional and danger is rarely taken seriously. From “flesh wounds” that aren’t quite as bad as they look to gloriously absurd misadventures at every turn, it’s a fast-paced, joyfully ridiculous night at the theatre you won’t want to miss.\nSJTC Subscriptions onsale now Regular: $143 | Senior: $131 | Student: $79\nSingle tickets onsale September 1st\nPerformances:\nWed, May 19 @ 7:30pm\nThurs, May 20 @ 7:30pm\nFri, May 21 @ 7:30pm\nSat, May 22 @ 2pm\nSat, May 22 @ 7:30pm\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t"
